=======================LockBox=====================================================================================

---------------------July 2012--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Description
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Application for secure storing user's secrets for Android

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Folder structure
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

doc: generated documentation
src: source files for application
res: resource files for android application
criptomini_libs: crypto libraries
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Build process
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Requirements: Apache Ant 1.6.0+, Android SDK API level 14+, TrustZone and Secure Storage need to be installed.
			  Secure Storage Service must be running
			  
			  Place cryptomini_libs on the device (connected to PC):
			  1. cd %platform_tools%
			  2. adb push LockBox_project_path\criptomini_libs\criptomini.so /data/local/ss_demo/
			  3. adb push LockBox_project_path\criptomini_libs\criptomini_jni.so /data/local/ss_demo/

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Android
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Make sure to add the location of the SDK's tools/ and platform-tools/ to PATH environment variable.
2. cd /LockBox
3. android update project -p .
4. ant clean
5. ant debug
6. Resulting LockBox-debug.apk and binaries will be placed in bin/ folder.
7. cd %platform-tools/%
8. adb install %LockBox_project_path%/bin/LockBox-debug.apk

====================================================================================================================